honor, viewed with awe, embellished, and revered; and may the
blessed name of holiness be hailed though it be higher (/ITOn Shabbat
Shuvah add:/XX by far) than all the blessings, songs, praises, and
consolations that we utter in this world. And say: Amen./PR

